A '''Request For Privacy''' was a document that the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] required [[Scout/Legends|scouts]] or other claimants to file in cases where information about a [[Planet/Legends|planet]] or [[Star system/Legends|system]] was to remain unavailable to the public. This usually only occurred when a military research base or similarly sensitive facility was to be built on the planet.

